First American’s Napolitano Leaves, N.Y. Post Reports

-- B y   J a m e s   K r a u s
-- 
2011-02-28T18:28:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/first-american-s-napolitano-leaves-n-y-post-reports-correct-.html
(Corrects title of Napolitano in first paragraph of story
first published on Feb. 24.)  Steven Napolitano, president of
First American Title Insurance Cos., New York division, left the
company Feb. 15 to go on administrative leave, the New York Post
reported, citing unidentified people.  Napolitano couldn’t be reached for comment and a
spokeswoman for the company declined to comment, the newspaper
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net  